# Pastel Cozy Journal-Themed Habit Tracking UI

Redesign the entire Rituals frontend with a **scrapbook / bullet journal aesthetic** — warm, cozy, and premium feeling. The UI will use pastel colors, sticky-note components, floating sticker decorations, and handwritten fonts.

